install rvm and ruby like this:

bash -s stable < <(curl -s https://raw.github.com/wayneeseguin/rvm/master/binscripts/rvm-installer)
source ~/.bash_profile
rvm install 1.9.2

checkout repo and install shitz:

git clone git@github.com:happstr/happstr.git
cd happstr
gem install bundler
bundle install

run sinatra:
rackup
